  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Staying at the <span>Sirkantähti Apartments gives you a choice to stay on bed and breakfast or upgrade to half board. </span></p>
<p><span>Enjoy a buffet style breakfast every morning in the main hotel restaurant (250 - 350 metres away). You'll have choices including fruit, yoghurt, toast, cereal, bacon, scrambled eggs, tea, coffee and fruit juice. There are </span><span>lots of nice restaurants to check out in town and Levi supermarket just over the road for any extras you might need. </span></p>
<p><span>Or, you can upgrade to half board where you'll have a buffet breakfast, plus dinner in the <a data-udi="umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf}" title="Sirkantahti Hotel">Sirkantähti Hotel</a> Restaurant. Dinner is buffet style, with three courses which include meat and vegetable options, plus a salad bar. </span>The restaurant is open for dinner from 5pm - 7pm in December and 6pm - 9pm in January and February. The hotels Bar &amp; Café are open from 9am - 1am.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music. Please also note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option. </p>
<p>New Year Gala Dinner includes a glass of sparkling wine. <span></span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
