  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The Sirkantähti Apartments are in a great location at the top of <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Levi</a>'s main street. You'll be close to the centre of town and the ski slopes, with your own private space to come back to after days spent exploring the area. Book with bed and breakfast included and check out the local restaurants in town in the evenings - there are plenty to choose from. The supermarket is nearby so you'll be able to stock up on any extras you need.</span></p>
<p><span>The apartments are a great choice for families and small groups. They all have a small living area and kitchenette, but the best part is that every apartment has it's own en suite sauna - nothing beats coming back to a hot sauna after a day out in the snow! </span></p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Located close to the resort centre, you have great access to all of the exciting excursions and activities Levi has to offer. Enjoy the well groomed slopes at the Levi Ski Resort or book onto one of our optional extra excursions -choose from a snowmobile safari, reindeer and husky excursions or a Northern lights adventure. Our excursions are a great way to immerse yourself in the Finnish traditions and learn about the Sami way of life. </p>
<h2>Well equipped apartments</h2>
<p>The apartments are nicely furnished and come equipped with everything you need for your stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland.</a> After a day of exploring the Arctic, hang your coats up to dry in the drying cupboard and warm up in your own private sauna. The apartments have their own equipped kitchenette so you can cook tasty meals from the comfort of your apartment, making these a great choice for groups of families and friends looking for accommodation on bed and breakfast in <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>. Take the fuss out of meal times and opt into half board, meals are taken at the <a data-udi="umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf}" title="Sirkantahti Hotel">Sirkantahti Hotel</a> - each day you can enjoy an extensive buffet breakfast and a varied evening meal served buffet style. </p>]]></description>
