  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studio Apartments</strong> are about 20m² and sleep two people. These apartments have a small lounge, kitchenette and a ski equipment locker. These apartments are mainly situated in the LeviStar Buildings 1 and 3, about 350 -350 metres from the main building. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Mini fridge</li>
<li>Kettle</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Clothes drying cupboard</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Please note that the apartments do not include Wi-Fi. </em></p>]]></roomsDescription>
